ass=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531250/extras/311222a1c7ba8bf284bfde6e08df053f.poster.avif?t=1727784928\" width=620 height=182 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531250/extras/311222a1c7ba8bf284bfde6e08df053f.webm?t=1727784928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1531250/extras/311222a1c7ba8bf284bfde6e08df053f.mp4?t=1727784928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Place traps and barricades to defend your castle!</strong></h2><br>Use these wisely to funnel and confuse the invaders. Wreak havoc amongst their ranks and break up their carefully manicured ranks!<br><br><strong>Become a champion to save the kingdom!</strong><br><br>Do you have what it takes to save the land? Jump right in and enjoy a set of procedurally generated roguelike turn-based battles like no other! Every battle fought is unique.",
